(4737, 'Techeiles Trek', 'Mishpacha Magazine Jan 22, 2014', NULL, 'http://tekhelet.com/pdf/TecheilesTrek.pdf', '', 'According to the Ramban, techeiles is supposed to take us on an inner journey from the sea to the sky to the throne of Hashem. That journeywas aborted some 1,300 years ago, when the knowledge of how to produce techeiles was lost. But thanks to a few people on a mission, techeiles is back - and if you look closely, you may discover that sky-blue thread hanging from a pair of tzitzis near you.', 'Greenspan', '2014-01-22', '12220244', 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
