(4876, 'L\'étude de la pourpre: histoire d\'une couleur, chimie et expérimentations', 'Preistoria AlpinaSuppl. 1, v. 40 (2004)pp. 133-160Trento 2005ISSN 0393-0157Museo Tridentino di Scienze Naturali', 'French', 'https://thelibrary.tekhelet.com/./uploads/Letude_de_la_pourpre_histoire_dune_coule.pdf', 'Article', 'The paper mainly deals with the discovery of the chemical structure of purple-dye. Other topics concern shell species, geographical distribution of purple production and archaeological remains. Different techniques of dyeing are described.', 'Murex, Purple', '2004-01-01', '14.3 KB', 4, 1, 1, '2021-09-23 07:23:10', '2021-09-23 07:23:10'),
